  <h2>Preventive maintenance keeps the doors open</h2>
  <p>The cheapest refrigeration failure is the one that never happens. Our commercial PM program runs quarterly or monthly by equipment load and covers:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Condenser coil cleaning,</strong> the single biggest failure cause in Tampa humidity and kitchen-grease environments.</li>
    <li><strong>Evaporator coil inspection</strong> and defrost-cycle verification.</li>
    <li><strong>Door-gasket inspection</strong> and replacement, critical for energy and food safety.</li>
    <li><strong>Condensate drain flushing</strong> and pan treatment.</li>
    <li><strong>Temperature calibration</strong> at rack controllers and individual cases.</li>
    <li><strong>Compressor amp draw and oil check,</strong> plus a refrigerant leak scan.</li>
    <li><strong>A written report</strong> for your health-inspector records.</li>
  </ul>

